quran[42]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,"O (Annabi Muhammadu) saɣim o nini ni, ka lebi biri"
  80,2,Domin zom kana o sani na zuɣu
  80,3,(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Bo n-leei baŋsi a ni di yi pa shɛli o naan niŋ kasi
  80,4,"Bee ka o wum a wa’azu, ka wa’azu maa niŋ o anfaani"
  80,5,Amaa! Ninvuɣu so ŋun mali buni maa
  80,6,Ka a zaɣisim be o ni
  80,7,Tɔ! Bo n-leei yɛn niŋ a chuuta o yi bi niŋ kasi
  80,8,Amaa! Ŋun kana a sani n-ti bɔri yomyom’ maa
  80,9,Ka o nyɛla ŋun zɔri Naawuni
  80,10,Ka a nyɛla ŋun yi o yɛla ni
  80,11,Haifa! Achiika! Di nyɛla teebu
  80,12,"Dinzuɣu, ŋun bɔra ŋun zaŋ li n-teei o maŋa"
  80,13,Di bela kundi shɛŋa din mali jilma la puuni
  80,14,"Ka di nyɛ bɛ ni duhi shɛli, ka nyɛla din mali kasi"
  80,15,Ka di be Malaaikanim’ ban sabri (ninsalinim’) tuuntumsa nuu ni
  80,16,"Darzanima, ban doli Naawuni zaligu"
  80,17,"Bɛ narim ninsala (chɛfura), bo n- leei chɛ ka o niŋ gutulunsi"
  80,18,Ni bimbo ka O (Naawuni) nam o
  80,19,"Ni maniyyi (dablim kom) ka O nam o, ka nam O saɣisi"
  80,20,Din nyaaŋa ka O balgi soli n-ti o
  80,21,"Din nyaaŋa, ka O chɛ ka o kpi, ka zaŋ o niŋ gballi ni"
  80,22,"Din nyaaŋa, O yi bɔra, ka O lahi yiɣisi o"
  80,23,Haifa! O (ninsala) bi tum Naawuni ni puhi o shɛli niŋbu
  80,24,"Dinzuɣu, ninsala yulmi o bindirgu"
  80,25,Achiika! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) kpaai la kom na (sagbana ni) kpaabu ni yɛlimaŋli
  80,26,"Din nyaaŋa, ka Ti chɛ ka tiŋgbani tahibɔɣi, bɔɣibu ni yɛlimaŋli"
  80,27,"Din nyaaŋa, ka Ti chɛ ka bimbilima yi di puuni na"
  80,28,Ni inabi (sinsaba) mini momaha
  80,29,Ni zaituun mini dobino
  80,30,Ni puri din laɣim tihi pam
  80,31,Ni binwola mini biŋkobri bindira
  80,32,"Ka di nyɛla nyεɣisim n-ti ya, n-ti pahi yi biŋkobri"
  80,33,"Dinzuɣu, tahigu din pahi ayi yi ti kana"
  80,34,Dindali ka ninsala yɛn ti zɔri ka chɛri o mabia
  80,35,Ni o ba mini o ma
  80,36,Ni o paɣa mini o bihi
  80,37,"Dindali maa, bɛ puuni ninvuɣu yino kam daa ti yεn malila yɛli shɛli din saɣindi o"
  80,38,"Dindali maa, ninvuɣu shɛba nina yɛn ti malila neesim"
  80,39,"Ka nyɛla din lara, ka mali suhupɛlli"
  80,40,"Dindali maa mi, taŋkpagbilgu yɛn ti limsila shɛba nina polo"
  80,41,Ka zimsim ŋari li
  80,42,"Bannim’ maa n-nyɛ chɛfurinima, ka nyɛ bibiɛhi"